content: You CAN'T SEARCH for conjugated verbs like "prends", "fait" etc. which is a huge downside since otherwise the glossary is quite good.
Excellent! Worth every penny. (At first it was stopping at conjugations, which I reported. Works fine now after a phone restart. Android 7.1.1)

App is pretty basic. There are no settings to change font, option to contact the owner, offer suggestions or anything similar. I also expected to be able to click on the words in the definitions for translation instead of having to type them.
Good app with decent service. I reported problems and they fixed them quickly. They listen to you and respond. A product behind a group of staff who care shall win their business!
